# >>> SECRETS BACKUP CONVENTION <<<
# After you create your real .env from this template:
# whenever you CHANGE a value in .env, back it up off-machine:
#     python tools/drive/backup_secrets.py
# Why: .env is gitignored, so the host machine is the only copy of live keys.
# >>> END <<<

